and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of the premium index over the previous funding period. The exchange applies a dampening mechanism when rates exceed ±0.75% to prevent extreme funding costs. Funding payments are automatically debited or credited to trader accounts based on position size and direction, with long positions paying when rates are positive and receiving when negative."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
